Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.98,Post,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640.667,567.333)\fad(400,0)\c&HE5E6E8&\bord3}武藏号距浦贺水道仅剩20分钟航程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二号 三号 四号舰无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一号舰最快只能拿出6节航速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样下去的话 二十分钟后武藏号就进入浦贺水道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重复 所有人请立刻离船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重复 所有人请立刻离船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}校长 晴风号发来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是晴风号舰长 岬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望您批准我舰对武藏号执行拦截计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全班同学都已同意本计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让我们试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}横须贺女子海洋学校校长宗谷真雪同意该计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 你们只有一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}陆地方面正在准备解决这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因此你们不需要反复攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要能拖住它5分钟 不 3分钟就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 宗谷校长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号已经瘫痪了三艘蓝色人鱼的舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让晴风号单舰拦截这实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}20分钟后武藏号将进入浦贺水道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 宗谷监察官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只靠我们 确实没法拦下武藏号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是拖延时间还是做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且香香…武藏号的舰长仍然困守在舰桥里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们能联系上武藏号的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她接收不到无线信号 我们通过灯光信号联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}岬舰长 同意你舰接近武藏号执行拦截计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始吧 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}猎人肯定比猎物强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 请下达指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航向30度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航向30度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距离武藏号30
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都告诉过她们别过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉 瞄准武藏号主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要把武藏号拦下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小依 与武藏号并行的时候发射所有鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我梦寐以求的全雷发射…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发射的机会恐怕只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必须靠这一次机会拦下她们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}集中攻击舰尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了 我一定会打中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小理 小代 做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明 难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标 武藏号舰尾 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瞄准点 武藏号舰尾 一发都别打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 没点效果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漂亮 全部命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号 速度下降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们要开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人准备承受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰尾烟幕施放器故障
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}深水炸弹投射器受损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五号仓库发生火情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正在灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这 这才一炮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 彻底坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无线通讯设备故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无线设备也坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 我们迟滞她们了五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃 迅速离开武藏号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一号炮输弹机故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烹炊室发生火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是武藏号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前进方向被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阻止炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然晴风号就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冷静点 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轮机长 水啊 有水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说什么 我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 左舷轮机室进水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把能找来的水泵都带来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可别让锅炉的火灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连轮机室都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 要不要让大家做弃舰准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开什么玩笑 现在还逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇要是被吃掉了头的话 想活都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 都怪我操舵技术不精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人准备弃舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃 右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}后方发现舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是蓝色人鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已确认识别信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比睿号 舞风号 滨风号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}海军上将施佩伯爵号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天神号？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我们学校的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:27.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,531.333)}赴汤蹈火的最终之战！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}古庄教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还好我们赶上了 抱歉来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}野间同学 告诉他们无线电坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸子 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你来救我们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还人情的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有大家的帮助 我们还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我完全赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}改变计划 准备登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵号在询问我们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们准备强行登上武藏号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请求掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请求掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是这样 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来我们将掩护晴风号实施强行登舰计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天神号 施佩伯爵号从武藏号右舷方向开火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比睿号 舞风号 滨风号从左舷方向攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}支援晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各舰做好突击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标 武藏号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起风了 是希望之风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全舰突击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}转告各舰 千万不要打中了武藏号的舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得找个机会才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个能派得上用场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火箭弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明石号给我们装上的 说可能会有用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开到武藏号前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰 舰首前面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知床同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前进 目标武藏号前方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是要开到武藏号前面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别让武藏号攻击晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尽量吸引对方的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧 晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉 抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火箭弹已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速前进 右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰尾对准武藏号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速前进 右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉 准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉 倾注你的灵魂
