Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃 右满舵 目标武藏号的右舷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舵 舵轮转不动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 船舵中弹 无法操舵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有阻力伞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小萌 小百准备阻力伞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经绑好了 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把它从右舷后方扔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}转向了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了 我们反转了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别管发动机了 千万别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到武藏号了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分离阻力伞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备承受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 突击成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救援部队 准备接舷登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我上 夺舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就待在这里 毕竟是舰长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧 岬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我懂你 你的想法都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的老朋友小白 你太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 我们又不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终于见到你了 明明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明也真是的 太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作战结束 所有舰船即刻返还横须贺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈 可惜这回你没能创造传说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的学生替我做成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是地面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总觉得还有些不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来人扶一扶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别沉啊
